modName: Lady of Death Set with TBBP
descriptionHtml:
This mod is a replacer of the main body mesh with TBBP added. You need the original [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/13761]Lady of Death Set for CBBE V3 by newermind43[/url] for the full set and esp.

Required: [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/34713]TBBP animations[/url] also a skeleton with TBBP, such as [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/26800]XP32 Maximum Skeleton[/url] OR [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/16712] Custom Skeleton Replacers[/url].

Not recomended to use increased size, TBBP clothing/armor may not fit correctly.
